>>>>>>> There isn’t a cure for diabetes right now. But our scientists across
the UK are working hard in the lab and pushing boundaries to one day get us
>>>>>>> * ### What are immunotherapies and how could they help
>>>>>>> Immunotherapy targets the immune system to prevent or halt Type 1
