>>>>>>> * ### What causes Type 1 diabetes?
>>>>>>> Our immune system normally protects us against infection and illness.
But in Type 1 diabetes, the immune system attacks the cells in the pancreas
that make insulin. Scientists are working hard to find out what causes this to
>>>>>>> ## Shining a light on research gaps
>>>>>>> * ### Mental health and emotional wellbeing
>>>>>>> We've spoken to thousands of people whose lives are affected by
diabetes. They told us that too often the emotional and mental support they
need is missing, and scientists are joining the fight to change this.
